  "overview": [
    "Opened in 1967, the Recreation and Athletics Complex is the heart of varsity and recreational sports at Concordia’s Loyola Campus. It features the NHL-standard Ed Meagher Arena, a 4,000-seat stadium, gymnasium and two outdoor turf fields.",
